txt.en: 'The yells of the Gundabad can be heard rerverberating off the walls of this cavernous mine'
'The Gundabad protect the valuable resources contained within Glimmerdeep by any means necessary'
'The discontent between this unorganized group is what is holding them back from taking the mine decisively'
'A gate blocks the only span across the chasm!'
'This mine cart should be able to break the gate!'
'Puny little [placeholder], you're no match for Blogdob!'
'Give us what you have taken from us!'
'Glimmerdeep was all mine for the taking, this can't be....'
'Shinies and wealth. That all we care for'
